import React from "react";
import {Box, Typography, styled, Button, Stack} from "@mui/material"
import Background from "./../Images/HeroBackground.jpg";
import Handy from "./../Images/handy.png";

const RightBox = styled(Box)({
    backgroundImage:`url(${Background})`, 
    backgroundAttachment: "fixed",
    backgroundSize: "80%",
    minHeight:"80vh",
    
});

const Header = styled(Stack)({
    background: "#BFD200",
    textAlign: "left",
});

//StyledBox als Parent von LeftBox und RIghtBox?
export default function Hero() {
    return (
        <Box bgcolor="black">
            <Stack direction="row">
                <Box component="img"
                    src={require("./../Images/handy.png")}
                    flex={1}>
                    <Header sx={{minHeight:"60px"}}></Header>
                </Box>
                <RightBox flex={2}>
                    <Typography>
                        COACHING MADE EASY
                    </Typography>
                    <Typography>
                        MINIMALER AUFWAND.
                    </Typography>
                    <Typography>
                        MAXIMALER ERFOLG.
                    </Typography>
                    <Typography>
                        Weil der Trainerjob Spa√ü machen soll!
                    </Typography>
                    <Button>
                        LOS GEHT'S
                    </Button>
                <Stack direction="row">
                    <Stack direction="column">
                        <Typography>
                            6.000+
                        </Typography>
                        <Typography>
                            Trainer
                        </Typography>
                    </Stack>
                    <Stack direction="column">
                        <Typography>
                            5 Mio
                        </Typography>
                        <Typography>
                            Trainings
                        </Typography>
                    </Stack>
                    <Stack direction="column">
                        <Typography>
                            3.000+
                        </Typography>
                        <Typography>
                            Spiele
                        </Typography>
                    </Stack>
                </Stack>
            </RightBox>
            </Stack>
 
        </Box>
    )
}
